From the balance sheet provided:
- Initial value of Retained Earnings (as of 2023-12-31): 0.00
- End value of Retained Earnings (as of 2024-02-02): 112375.10

This indicates that during this period, the company generated a profit of 112,375.10 that was retained in the business.
